stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Pending: POST /workflows
    Pending --> Running: POST /workflows/:id/run
    Running --> Running: Execute step
    Running --> Completed: All steps succeed
    Running --> Compensating: Step fails
    Compensating --> Failed: LIFO compensation
    Completed --> [*]
    Failed --> [*]

    note right of Running
        GalacticCommerce example:
        ProcessPayment → ReserveInventory → SendConfirmation
    end note

    note right of Compensating
        On failure: RefundPayment
        ReleaseInventory (LIFO rollback)
    end note
